message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present our premium product, which I believe would significantly enhance your operations or personal endeavors. Given its exceptional value and utility, I estimate its worth to be $12000 to you. Considering this, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $10000. This offer is tailored to ensure you receive the best value while also allowing me to maximize the return on my investment. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to facilitate this transaction.
